{"tid":1428282,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"和理非升級：罷買、快閃鳩嗚？","createTime":"2019-08-07T09:19:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T09:41:16.000Z","uid":258267,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"985e132e6086a244f9cc2f52493ccd3a6b6f91ba","tid":1428282,"uid":258267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:19:36.000Z","msg":"多謝大家願意為香港罷一日工。<br />\n但係罷工始終唔係咁易長期作戰，罷買不但可以長久，而且可以對準紅企，顯示經濟影響力，會唔會真係試下執行？<br />\n方案可以係逢一、三、五罷食/買一個紅色企業，而且仲吹雞去唔同區店鋪快閃叫口號抗議，咁先會見到個效果。<br />\n<br />\n例如<br />\n星期日講定星期一八點：<br />\n大家樂-北角xx，黃大仙xx，天水圍xx。<br />\n認同請推同熱烈討論。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7852e14d6f61d93fb67cba30f5e640538562cacb","tid":1428282,"uid":264246,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:21:11.000Z","msg":"長期星期五罷買"},{"pid":"d801a2a7cbba69a8734643249b6d1118189e0cd9","tid":1428282,"uid":258267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:21:47.000Z","msg":"自推，勇武升級和理非都要跟上呀！"},{"pid":"bcc41b24b08a1db48783c6f081ccca7e93e8e7c3","tid":1428282,"uid":258267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:22:39.000Z","msg":"自推，一齊傾下下一步點行！"},{"pid":"aa502bc5047802438d7a93cb0e311f5640f88496","tid":1428282,"uid":280572,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:22:45.000Z","msg":"我覺得快閃鳩嗚有用<br />\n譬如今日星期三8點 大家一齊去ssp買雷射筆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd4f82a86664f801f9a0e1facd88ceb0e2323a89","tid":1428282,"uid":38109,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:22:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" cl